metadata.description:
In an endless pursuit of perfection, New Eden’s most successful beauty engineer Leon finds one art masterpiece that changes his life. This is an origin story of Mona, cyber girl on a mission. 
 
 «Monaverse x Cryptelligence: Issue#1» is the very first comic book released in the ‘New Eden Chronicles’ series, in what will become an ongoing and lasting subscription for Monaverse and Cryptelligence NFT holders. 
 
 This issue will become available for claim soon and can be used to participate in holder raffles hosted by Cryptelligence or Monaverse.
metadata.name: Monaverse x Cryptelligence: issue#1
